    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "胡亥不聽。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "而遣御史曲宮乘傳之代，令蒙毅曰：「先主欲立太子而卿難之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "今丞相以卿為不忠，罪及其宗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "朕不忍，乃賜卿死，亦甚幸矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
