        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "卿其圖之！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "毅對曰：「以臣不能得先主之意，則臣少宦，順幸沒世。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "可謂知意矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "以臣不知太子之能，則太子獨從，周旋天下，去諸公子絕遠，臣無所疑矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "夫先主之舉用太子，數年之積也，臣乃何言之敢諫，何慮之敢謀！",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "非敢飾辭以避死也，為羞累先主之名，願大夫為慮焉，使臣得死情實。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "且夫順成全者，道之所貴也；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "刑殺者，道之所卒也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "昔者秦穆公殺三良而死，罪百里奚而非其罪也，故立號曰『繆』。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "昭襄王殺武安君白起。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "楚平王殺伍奢。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "吳王夫差殺伍子胥。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "此四君者，皆為大失，而天下非之，以其君為不明，以是籍於諸侯。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "故曰『用道治者不殺無罪，而罰不加於無辜』。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "唯大夫留心！」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "使者知胡亥之意，不聽蒙毅之言，遂殺之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
