    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "二世又遣使者之陽周，令蒙恬曰：「君之過多矣，而卿弟毅有大罪，法及內史。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "恬曰：「自吾先人，及至子孫，積功信於秦三世矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "今臣將兵三十餘萬，身雖囚系，其勢足以倍畔，然自知必死而守義者，不敢辱先人之教，以不忘先主也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "昔周成王初立，未離襁緥周公旦負王以朝，卒定天下。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "及成王有病甚殆，公旦自揃其爪以沈於河，曰：『王未有識，是旦執事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "有罪殃，旦受其不祥。』",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "乃書而藏之記府，可謂信矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "及王能治國，有賊臣言：『周公旦欲為亂久矣，王若不備，必有大事。』",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "王乃大怒，周公旦走而奔於楚。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "成王觀於記府，得周公旦沈書，乃流涕曰：『孰謂周公旦欲為亂乎！』",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "殺言之者而反周公旦。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
