          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "臣故曰過可振而諫可覺也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "察於參伍，上聖之法也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "凡臣之言，非以求免於咎也，將以諫而死，願陛下為萬民思從道也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "使者曰：「臣受詔行法於將軍，不敢以將軍言聞於上也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "蒙恬喟然太息曰：「我何罪於天，無過而死乎？」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "良久，徐曰：「恬罪固當死矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "起臨洮屬之遼東，城塹萬餘里，此其中不能無絕地脈哉？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "此乃恬之罪也。」",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "乃吞藥自殺。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "translator": "Garrett M. Petersen (2025)",
              "model": "grok-code-fast-1",
              "reviewed": true
            }
          ]
        }
